OL,3,CFormer Archbishop describes calls to
OL,4,Cresign as a 'nightmare'
OL,6,FThe former Archbishop of Wales has
OL,7,Fdescribed his decision to step down as
OL,8,F"very painful".
OL,10,FAndrew John told BBC Radio Cymru that
OL,11,Fcalls for his resignation were a
OL,12,F"nightmare", but it is "right to give
OL,13,Fsomeone else the opportunity to take
OL,14,Fresponsibility for the future".
OL,16,FMr John announced he was retiring as
OL,17,FArchbishop with immediate effect at
OL,18,Fthe end of June. He also confirmed he
OL,19,Fwould stand down as Bishop of Bangor.
