OL,3,CFormer Archbishop describes calls to
OL,4,Cresign as a 'nightmare'
OL,6,FThe announcement came after two
OL,7,Fsummary reviews were published on
OL,8,Fbehaviour at Bangor Cathedral, which
OL,9,Fincluded details of "inappropriate
OL,10,Fbehaviour", "blurred sexual
OL,11,Fboundaries" and "excessive alcohol
OL,12,Fconsumption".
OL,14,FThe Church in Wales has now called for
OL,15,Fa number of additional reviews and
OL,16,Finvestigations of Bangor Cathedral and
OL,17,Fthe diocese.
OL,19,FThere is no suggestion that the former
OL,20,FArchbishop acted inappropriately.
