OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F469A1751984184
OL,3,CFormer Archbishop describes calls to
OL,4,Cresign as a 'nightmare'
OL,6,F"Being present at the meeting and
OL,7,Fhaving people more or less calling for
OL,8,Fyour resignation was like being in a
OL,9,Fnightmare," he told BBC Wales.
OL,11,F"It pains me that these things
OL,12,Fhappened under my watch and I'll have
OL,13,Fto live with that," he said.
OL,15,F"Bangor is a fantastic diocese.
OL,17,F"The damage done to the diocese,
OL,18,Fbecause I didn't pay enough attention
OL,19,Fto problems, is a burden I'll carry."
